txt.en: 'Many foes still wander throughout Talath Úrui. If you find yourself travelling in these lands, you should defeat any foes you come across.'
Bregdal, a soldier of Gondor, has scouted Talath Úrui and found many foes still remain.
You have dealt a mighty blow to all foes in Talath Úrui.
A notice is pinned to the board, signed by Bregdal:\n\n'Many foes still wander throughout Talath Úrui. A brave adventurer is needed to defeat foes in these lands.'
Bregdal has asked you to defeat foes in Talath Úrui.
